 spectrum of SN 2020ank exhibits a close spectral resemblance with\nthat of fast-evolving SN 2010gx. The absorption features of SN 2020ank are\nblueshifted compared to Gaia16apd, suggesting a higher expansion velocity. The\nspectral similarity with SN 2010gx and comparatively faster spectral evolution\nthan PTF12dam (a slow-evolving SLSN) indicate the fast-evolving behavior of SN\n2020ank.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2020 18:02:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Jan 2021 07:35:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
