 and instrument designs, mission parameters, and\nscience performance are described. VTXO development was supported as one of the\nselected 2018 NASA Astrophysics SmallSat Study (AS$^3$) missions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2020 20:29:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-01"}
