ated by the new and existing algorithms, one can now\nconstruct the general solution of the corresponding Riccati equation to obtain\na one-parameter family of geometries for each input solution. We discuss the\nregularity of the resulting solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Dec 2020 07:13:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Aug 2021 19:17:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
