total\nnumber of words to be analyzed is lower. Whatever the case, authors recommend a\nrevision of the results obtained by experts in the area to avoid inaccurate\nresults and get the most meaningful information.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Dec 2020 11:33:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-01"}
